              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character has no sense of rhythm or pitch, turning any attempt at a lute tune or harvest dance into a spectacle of awkwardness. Their singing clears out taverns faster than a tax collector\u2019s arrival. Even clapping along to a bard\u2019s song is a disaster, throwing everyone off beat. Their lack of coordination spills over into other delicate tasks, too.",
